                <h3 class="subheading">Škoda Kylaq</h3>
            
                <ul>
                    <li>1.0L TSI petrol engine (115PS, 178Nm)</li>
                    <li>6-speed manual or 6-speed auto transmission</li>
                    <li>0-100 km/h in 10.5 seconds, top speed 188 km/h</li>
                    <li>Fuel economy: 19.05 to 19.68 kmpl</li>
                </ul>

                <p><span class="font-weight-700">Performance standpoint:</span></p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Nexon</strong> offers more engine variety (petrol, diesel, EV)</li>
                    <li><strong>Kylaq</strong> provides refinement and efficiency at lower end</li>
                </ul>

                <div class="div-line"></div>
                <h2 class="subheading">Cabin Comfort & Tech</h2>

                <h3 class="subheading">Tata Nexon</h3>
            
                <ul>
                    <li>Digital instrument cluster and touchscreen infotainment (Harman in EV)</li>
                    <li>iRA connected-car tech</li>
                    <li>Voice-controlled sunroof, JBL sound system, wireless charging</li>
                    <li>Ventilated leatherette seats, cooled glovebox, rear AC vents</li>
                    <li>382L boot space</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="subheading">Škoda Kylaq</h3>
               
                <ul>
                    <li>Ambient lighting, metal accents</li>
                    <li>Ventilated driver and passenger seats (power-adjustable in higher variants)</li>
                    <li>Clever design touches like ticket holders and seatback phone pockets</li>
                    <li>10-inch touchscreen with wireless Apple/Android Auto</li>
                    <li>Wireless phone charger, dual-zone auto climate with air purifier</li>
                    <li>446L boot (expandable to 1,265L)</li>
